{"snp5.17:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.17 ","snp5.17:0.2":"Pingiyamanavapuccha ","snp5.17:1.1":"“Jinnohamasmi abalo vitavanno, ","snp5.17:1.2":"(iccayasma pingiyo) ","snp5.17:1.3":"Netta na suddha savanam na phasu; ","snp5.17:1.4":"Maham nassam momuho antarava, ","snp5.17:1.5":"Acikkha dhammam yamaham vijannam; ","snp5.17:1.6":"Jatijaraya idha vippahanam”. ","snp5.17:2.1":"“Disvana rupesu vihannamane, ","snp5.17:2.2":"(pingiyati bhagava) ","snp5.17:2.3":"Ruppanti rupesu jana pamatta; ","snp5.17:2.4":"Tasma tuvam pingiya appamatto, ","snp5.17:2.5":"Jahassu rupam apunabbhavaya”. ","snp5.17:3.1":"“Disa catasso vidisa catasso, ","snp5.17:3.2":"Uddham adho dasa disa imayo; ","snp5.17:3.3":"Na tuyham adittham asutam amutam, ","snp5.17:3.4":"Atho avinnatam kincanamatthi loke; ","snp5.17:3.5":"Acikkha dhammam yamaham vijannam, ","snp5.17:3.6":"Jatijaraya idha vippahanam”. ","snp5.17:4.1":"“Tanhadhipanne manuje pekkhamano, ","snp5.17:4.2":"(pingiyati bhagava) ","snp5.17:4.3":"Santapajate jarasa parete; ","snp5.17:4.4":"Tasma tuvam pingiya appamatto, ","snp5.17:4.5":"Jahassu tanham apunabbhavaya”ti. ","snp5.17:4.6":"Pingiyamanavapuccha solasama. "}